    <item>
      <title>中国将人民币中间价设定为2023年以来最低，绿灯亮起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-cuts-yuan-fix-to-weakest-since-2023-greenlighting-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将人民币每日参考汇率下调至 2023 年底以来的最低水平，这表明在美元飙升、人民币贬值后，央行允许人民币贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-cuts-yuan-fix-to-weakest-since-2023-greenlighting-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 01:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选威胁林吉特债券市场 遭遇 2020 年以来最严重抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-win-to-worsen-biggest-selloff-in-ringgit-bonds-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普有望成为下一任美国总统，马来西亚债券收益率与美国国债收益率一同上升，因此马来西亚债券变得容易受到进一步资金外流的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-win-to-worsen-biggest-selloff-in-ringgit-bonds-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 01:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡特朗普的影响，大选震动后油价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡唐纳德·特朗普大选胜利和美国原油库存增加可能带来的影响，油价在周三经历了过山车式波动后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后亚洲股市失去方向：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡特朗普第二次担任总统及其提高关税的承诺所带来的影响，亚洲基准股票指数在涨跌之间波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
